productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Albertina has one of these. She works as a gardener and she says it looks humongous.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
i use it never when i'm in my hotel.
i use it this time when i'm in my port-a-potty.
one of my hobbies is mushroom cultivation. and when i'm cultivating mushrooms this works great.
